title: Dawn to Dusk Arizona

address.street: Pemberton Trailhead, McDowell Mountain Regional Park

description: Dawn to Dusk Arizona is an endurance mountain bike event where solos, duos, and teams ride from sunrise to sunset on the super-fun Pemberton loop in McDowell Mountain Regional Park.
course: The course starts and ends at the Pemberton loop trailhead. The route takes you in a counter-clockwise direction over 15.4 miles. Check ou the mtbproject link at: http://www.mtbproject.com/trail/2501604.
registration: Early Registration ends on October 1. The t-shirt deadline is November 26. Information and registration at: http://ziarides.com/event-register/dawn-dusk-arizona/,
notes: The event is a relay on a 15.4 course. Riders can sign up as a solo, duo team, 4-person team, and a corporate team of 7.
